{"tid":1214003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[1115]未知開唔開會，建議大家去搭地鐵先","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:40:29.000Z","uid":56076,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c71f61d0aa184989a01115d78ba1921ddb62e2d6","tid":1214003,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"發夢過咗10:30啦，而且都有消息話未必今日開會<br />\n雖然主席隨時可以宣布開會，只要一個鐘之前通知便可。<br />\n<br />\n但係係冇確實時間嘅情況下，希望大家唔好坐以待斃，做啲有用嘅嘢！加上今日無論點都好都冇可能集得翻好似琴日咁多人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以目前Keep住市民alert係最重要！<br />\n唔可以俾班善忘嘅港豬當乜事都冇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然，大家都唔應該鬆懈！<br />\n<br />\n但有確實消息嘅時候先再過去金鐘好冇？<br />\n<br />\n一個鐘我相信大家可以有足夠時間搭其他交通工具趕過過去！"},{"pid":"bc8f3464b116df8de70a51c9e8e207a8ccbc223d","tid":1214003,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e2e476c49053254e46b9f9e5423e9932033b9a","tid":1214003,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}